WITH d_rank AS (
    SELECT ListingId, MlsNumber, AddressText, ListingInsertedDateMT, DENSE_RANK() OVER (PARTITION BY AddressText ORDER BY ListingId) drank
    FROM [realtor_lake].[dbo].[listings_silver]
    WHERE BuildingType = 'House'
)
SELECT *
FROM d_rank
WHERE AddressText = '104 West Creek Court|Chestermere, Alberta T1X1L8'
--WHERE drank > 1;
--PriceChangeDateTimeStampUTC, PriceChangeDateMT

SELECT 
 source_file, BuildingType, COUNT(1) cnt, CEILING(AVG(PriceUnformattedValue)) AS avg_price
FROM [realtor_lake].[dbo].[listings_bronze]
--WHERE [source_file] = '2023-08-26'
--   and buildingtype = 'House'
GROUP BY source_file, BuildingType
ORDER BY source_file DESC, BuildingType ASC
 ;

SELECT 
month, BuildingType, COUNT(1) cnt, CEILING(AVG(PriceUnformattedValue))  AS avg_price
FROM [realtor_lake].[dbo].[listings_bronze]
--WHERE [source_file] = '2023-08-26'
--   and buildingtype = 'House'
GROUP BY month, BuildingType
ORDER BY month DESC, BuildingType ASC
;

SELECT TOP 10
 last_modified_time, PriceChangeDateUTC
FROM [realtor_lake].[dbo].[listings_bronze];

SELECT 
 source_file, BuildingType, COUNT(1) cnt
FROM [realtor_lake].[dbo].[listings_silver]
--WHERE [source_file] = '2023-08-26' and buildingtype = 'House'
GROUP BY source_file, BuildingType
ORDER BY source_file DESC, BuildingType ASC
 ;

SELECT TOP 100 *
FROM listings_silver;
